00:33:35.200 --> 00:33:36.260
The Third Front was

00:33:36.400 --> 00:33:38.200
a military preparedness concept.

00:33:38.200 --> 00:33:39.240
In the late 1960s,

00:33:40.050 --> 00:33:41.110
to prepare for war,

00:33:41.130 --> 00:33:43.790
many important plants
from coastal cities were

00:33:43.880 --> 00:33:46.830
moved to Shaanxi, Gansu,
Ningxia, Qinghai,

00:33:47.060 --> 00:33:50.060
Yunnan, Guizhou, Sichuan,
and other inland regions.

00:33:55.750 --> 00:33:56.750
These plants

00:33:56.960 --> 00:33:59.960
covered aerospace, automotive,
metallurgy, chemicals,

00:33:59.960 --> 00:34:02.030
and even shipbuilding.

00:34:03.350 --> 00:34:04.160
Director Liu,

00:34:04.860 --> 00:34:06.660
why isn't our plant marked on it?

00:34:07.550 --> 00:34:08.510
Our plant was

00:34:08.860 --> 00:34:10.170
a military enterprise

00:34:10.760 --> 00:34:13.280
and also part of the Third Front system.

00:34:14.389 --> 00:34:15.270
Military plants

00:34:15.270 --> 00:34:17.770
must follow principles
of mountain proximity and concealment,

00:34:17.770 --> 00:34:20.900
with dispersed locations
and underground facilities.

00:34:21.590 --> 00:34:24.590
That was why we established it
in this mountain valley

00:34:24.920 --> 00:34:27.580
and how our East Chemical Plant
came into being.

00:34:27.590 --> 00:34:29.650
Since we were a classified facility,

00:34:30.340 --> 00:34:32.000
we wouldn't be marked on maps.

00:34:32.389 --> 00:34:34.520
Because we were a classified facility,

00:34:34.520 --> 00:34:36.600
we got this confidentiality manual.

00:34:37.360 --> 00:34:37.920
Here.

00:34:41.730 --> 00:34:42.989
Everyone, take a look.

00:34:43.800 --> 00:34:44.260
This...

00:34:45.179 --> 00:34:46.659
It's full of typos!

00:34:48.440 --> 00:34:49.670
These aren't typos,

00:34:50.070 --> 00:34:51.960
but the simplified characters
from the second version.

00:34:51.960 --> 00:34:54.139
It's understandable
that you don't recognize them.

00:34:54.139 --> 00:34:55.780
This confidential manual was

00:34:55.780 --> 00:34:57.860
printed in 1978,

00:34:57.890 --> 00:34:59.370
older than all of you.

00:35:00.380 --> 00:35:03.170
So when you were kids,

00:35:03.190 --> 00:35:05.390
your parents and teachers required you

00:35:05.440 --> 00:35:08.100
to tell outsiders
that we were a chemical plant.

00:35:10.590 --> 00:35:12.120
Let's get back to the point.

00:35:12.350 --> 00:35:15.460
Let's talk
about yesterday, today, and tomorrow.

00:35:17.760 --> 00:35:18.510
"Yesterday"

00:35:19.190 --> 00:35:21.190
represents our former generation.

00:35:24.130 --> 00:35:26.570
They built this place from scratch

00:35:27.230 --> 00:35:28.550
through relentless endeavor,

00:35:28.550 --> 00:35:30.510
contributing
to today's East Chemical Plant.

00:35:30.510 --> 00:35:32.770
[East Integrated Chemical Plant]

00:35:34.150 --> 00:35:36.150
Most of them

00:35:36.970 --> 00:35:39.370
dedicated their entire lives
to the plant,

00:35:39.460 --> 00:35:41.480
unable to return
to their hometowns in the end.

