After they passed away,

00:35:42.510 --> 00:35:45.480
they were buried
on the western hillside of our plant,

00:35:45.480 --> 00:35:48.690
with their tombstones
all facing the plant.

00:35:49.550 --> 00:35:50.550
And "today" is

00:35:50.680 --> 00:35:52.240
about my generation.

00:35:53.670 --> 00:35:55.510
As the second generation
of plant workers,

00:35:55.510 --> 00:35:57.760
for our national defense building,

00:35:58.110 --> 00:36:00.320
we've also worked hard

00:36:00.690 --> 00:36:01.890
to create greatness.

